{
  "texts": [
    "Once read, the user may engage with the message:",
    "Agents' Rule 3 (engagement with a message): the probability that an agent i shares a message from an agent j (i.e., republish the message identically at the next time step) depends on the difference of opinion o t i -o t j.",
    "In the literature, different functional forms for the probability of engagement have been proposed such that the exact form should be estimated empirically according to the kind of opinion space that is modeled.",
    "Also, n p i (t) and n s i (t), ν t i and Bn i will be estimated empirically.",
    "3.12 Opinions co-evolve with interaction networks in a feedback loop."
  ]
}